description:
This is a 343 minute workout called 'HGW Hot Girl Walk' from the channel Mia Lind.
The workout falls under Cardio/Walking.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You won't need any equipmentThe workout has a The Groove Session and The Mindful Walk vibe.
The The Groove Session vibe means Fun, fluid, expressive, completely in the moment. This is especially good for Days when you want to move intuitively and just vibe. The The Mindful Walk vibe means Meditative, story-driven, immersive. This is especially good for When you need fresh air, a change of pace, and mental clarity..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.
